snippet.title: ARCANE BLAST RELEASE TRAILER
snippet.description:
#gaming #indiegames #gamer 
Arcane Blast is a fast-paced, action-packed roguelike brimming with sorcery. Master the seven elements, combine them to achieve powerful reactions and face swarms of enemies to help feline Mage Adrian find his way home from a time dungeon.

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2628230/Arcane_Blast/
Twitter/X: https://x.com/proj_delivery
